{"id": 1737, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得城市生活中，实现哪些事情就可以称得上是“小确成就”了？", "description": "生活中的一些微型打怪升级活动。（题图来自：Pixabay）", "record_count": 4457, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170613144023o2MOwcU67DifvTE5.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-17T17:00:15Z", "options": [{"id": 214272, "content": "有自己的家。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055442}, {"id": 214273, "content": "好坏也罢 \n12小时后见 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055613}, {"id": 214274, "content": "很容易就能找朋友借到钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034260}, {"id": 215044, "content": "工作领域里有一片自己的小天地。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1060688}, {"id": 214028, "content": "安全感来自自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 945263}, {"id": 214284, "content": "在食堂点到好吃的饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 130761}, {"id": 215820, "content": "买东西不考虑价钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062689}, {"id": 214029, "content": "无论外界多么喧闹，我的内心就是平静如水的做自己的事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 467257}, {"id": 214030, "content": "去哪里都有朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041408}, {"id": 214286, "content": "有一个非常要好的朋友  能伴一生的那种", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058396}, {"id": 214032, "content": "实习单位每天都碰面的人迎面走来主动和你打招呼", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053135}, {"id": 214033, "content": "周末有可以散心的地方或者放松的场所", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92975}, {"id": 214289, "content": "上市公司CEO", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997643}, {"id": 215825, "content": "有一个自己的家，老婆孩子父母（自己买的房子）", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1062070}, {"id": 214034, "content": "交通便利", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92975}, {"id": 215826, "content": "有房哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053717}, {"id": 214035, "content": "投资五个亿，不能说小有成就，中等成就吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 126974}, {"id": 214291, "content": "有个很喜欢自己的人 能一直陪在身边", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981884}, {"id": 215315, "content": "找到好吃又便宜的餐馆。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1113262}, {"id": 214292, "content": "找到自己的定位", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799564}, {"id": 214038, "content": "有一个可以供自己肆无忌惮的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020904}, {"id": 214040, "content": "一到站台，地铁就到", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 535937}, {"id": 214296, "content": "三十而立，小小主管，已经去过别人向往而没有去过的地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 998458}, {"id": 214041, "content": "从白手赚到第一个三千万。", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 525787}, {"id": 214297, "content": "找到一个自己理想、快乐的工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1028360}, {"id": 214042, "content": "不牺牲物质价值，实现精神价值。\n不牺牲精神价值时，实现物质价值，不忘本心。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057763}, {"id": 214298, "content": "不纠结", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058439}, {"id": 214043, "content": "在自己的城市立足", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057097}, {"id": 214299, "content": "出门都有单车骑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046194}, {"id": 214044, "content": "我想 和她每天在一起 在她遇到麻烦 我可以贼屌的帮助她", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 716907}, {"id": 214300, "content": "女人，减肥一生的事业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058459}, {"id": 214046, "content": "早高峰开车，能抢在黄灯变红之前通过。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 254572}, {"id": 214047, "content": "35岁，学会了游泳", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055976}, {"id": 214303, "content": "有车有房有朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 600070}, {"id": 214304, "content": "小孩上学在家边", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058490}, {"id": 214049, "content": "和人都能良好沟通", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056255}, {"id": 214305, "content": "有一个想回的家，无论租或买", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058491}, {"id": 214306, "content": "有自己的房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058495}, {"id": 214562, "content": "和爱人一起睡觉吃饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059405}, {"id": 214051, "content": "成功与100个陌生人搭讪", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951396}, {"id": 214307, "content": "不再是月光族...", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058505}, {"id": 214052, "content": "可以一直弹吉他，可以闭着眼感受美好！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839522}, {"id": 214308, "content": "坚持一个好的习惯?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058508}, {"id": 214053, "content": "知道人性的懒惰，并用于面对和不断与之斗争，实际行动的斗争！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1047697}, {"id": 214054, "content": "有自在的一个地方", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051865}, {"id": 214310, "content": "车限行有急事的话，随时能找朋友换到车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72501}, {"id": 214055, "content": "工作舒心，居有定所，早睡早起，定时锻炼", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 169028}, {"id": 214311, "content": "买房", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050366}, {"id": 215079, "content": "身边的朋友不再为你担心，而你，开始有能力回馈父母", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1020849}, {"id": 214568, "content": "可以睡到自然醒", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059432}]}